 Strangers''\n|[[V\u00e9hicule Press]]\n|<ref name=\"Official\"/>\n|- style=\"background:transparent;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent\" |{{sort|20124|[[2012 in literature|2012]]}}\n|{{sortname|Andrew J.|Borkowski|nolink=1}}\n|''Copernicus Avenue''\n|[[Cormorant Books]]\n|<ref name=\"Official\"/>\n|- style=\"background:transparent;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent\" |{{sort|20125|[[2012 in literature|2012]]}}\n|{{sortname|Johanna|Skibsrud}}\n|''This Will Be Difficult to Explain''\n|Hamish Hamilton Canada\n|<ref name=\"Official\"/>\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:#B0C4DE\" |{{sort|20131|[[2013 in literature|2013]]}}\n|{{sortname|Rebecca|Lee|nolink=1}}\n|''Bobcat and other stories''\n|[[Hamish Hamilton]]\n|<ref name=\"Official\"/>\n|- style=\"background:lightgreen;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:lightgreen\" |{{sort|20132|[[2013 in literature|2013]]}}\n|{{sortname|Anton|Piatigorsky|nolink=1}}\n|''The Iron Bridge''\n|[[Goose Lane Editions]]\n|<ref name=\"Official\"/>\n|- style=\"background:lightgreen;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:lightgreen\" |{{sort|20133|[[2013 in literature|2013]]}}\n|{{sortname|John|Vigna|nolink=1}}\n|''Bull Head''\n|[[Arsenal Pulp Press]]\n|<ref name=\"Official\"/>\n|- style=\"background:transparent;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent\" |{{sort|20134|[[2013 in literature|2013]]}}\n|{{sortname|Paul|Marlowe|}}\n|''Ether Frolics''\n|[[Sybertooth]]\n|<ref name=\"Official\"/>\n|- style=\"background:transparent;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent\" |{{sort|20135|[[2013 in literature|2013]]}}\n|{{sortname|Yasuko|Thanh}}\n|''Floating Lik