eron Press]]\n| <ref name=armstrong>[http://www.winnipegfreepress.com/arts-and-life/entertainment/books/short-story-award-short-list-revealed-382561741.html \"Short-story award short list revealed\"]. ''[[Winnipeg Free Press]]'', June 11, 2016.</ref>\n|- style=\"background:transparent;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent\" |{{sort|20165|[[2016 in literature|2016]]}}\n|{{sortname|Hugh|Graham|Hugh Graham (writer)}}\n|''Last Words''\n|[[Exile Editions]]\n| <ref name=armstrong/>\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:#B0C4DE\" |{{sort|20171|[[2017 in literature|2017]]}}\n|{{sortname|Kris|Bertin}}\n|''Bad Things Happen''\n|[[Biblioasis]]\n|<ref name=bertin>[http://www.pentictonherald.ca/entertainment/national_entertainment/article_57ce21e0-c0be-5c3f-ab3e-6ecc693f737a.html \"Halifax author Kris Bertin wins $10,000 Danuta Gleed Literary Award\"]. ''Penticton Herald'', June 3, 2017.</ref>\n|- style=\"background:lightgreen;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:lightgreen\" |{{sort|20172|[[2017 in literature|2017]]}}\n|{{sortname|Kerry Lee|Powell}}\n|''Willem deKooning's Paintbrush''\n|[[HarperCollins]]\n|<ref name=bertin/>\n|- style=\"background:lightgreen;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:lightgreen\" |{{sort|20173|[[2017 in literature|2017]]}}\n|{{sortname|Laura|Trunkey}}\n|''Double Dutch''\n|Astoria\n|<ref name=bertin/>\n|- style=\"background:transparent;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent\" |{{sort|20174|[[2017 in literature|2017]]}}\n|{{sortname|Lyse|Champagne}}\n|''The Light That Remains''\n|Enfield & Wizenty\n|<ref name=bertin/>\n|- style=\"background:transparent;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent\" |{{sort|20175|[[2017 in litera