oast Books]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.biblioasis.com/terence-young |title=Biblioasis author Terence Young |publisher=Biblioasis |accessdate=20 December 2012 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110827025201/http://www.biblioasis.com/terence-young |archivedate=27 August 2011 |df=dmy }}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:transparent;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent;\" |{{sort|20034|[[2000 in literature|2001]]}}\n|{{sortname|Alexandra|Leggat}}\n|''Pull Gently, Tear Here''\n|[[Insomniac Press]]\n|- style=\"background:transparent;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:transparent;\" |{{sort|20034|[[2000 in literature|2001]]}}\n|{{sortname|Annabel|Lyon}}\n|''Oxygen''\n|[[McClelland & Stewart]]\n|- style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background:#B0C4DE;\"|{{sort|20021|[[2001 in literature|2002]]}}\n|{{sortname|Gloria|Sawai}}\n|''A Song for Nettie Johnson''\n|[[Coteau Books]]\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://gglivres.conseildesarts.ca/en/about-apropos/archives/2002/Winners/A%20Song%20for%20Nettie%20Johnson.aspx |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130115110647/http://gglivres.conseildesarts.ca/en/about-apropos/archives/2002/Winners/A%20Song%20for%20Nettie%20Johnson.aspx |url-status=dead |archive-date=15 January 2013 |title=A Song for Nettie Johnson |publisher=Canada Council for the Arts |accessdate=20 December 2012 }}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:lightgreen;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:lightgreen;\" |{{sort|20022|[[2001 in literature|2002]]}}\n|{{sortname|Rick|Maddocks}}\n|''Sputnik Diner''\n|[[Knopf Canada]]\n|- style=\"background:lightgreen;\"\n!scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:center; font-weight:normal; background-color:lightgreen;\" |{{sort|20023|[[2001 in literature|2002]]}}\n|{{sortname|Madeleine|Thien}}\n|''Simple Recipes''\n|[[Littl